# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:43
translate spanish hwb_s15b_cec47e81:

    # "Beyond them, traffic mercifully lets up some. Not because there are fewer cars - there are more cars than rocks to be seen."
    "Más allá, el tráfico, por suerte, se alivia un poco. No porque haya menos autos — hay más autos que rocas a la vista."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:45
translate spanish hwb_s15b_755acf70:

    # "But a lot of those are pulled off on the shoulder, or cramped into parking lots. Nearly every inch of pavement that doesn’t have a car on it has a person instead."
    "Pero muchos de ellos están estacionados en la banquina, o apretados en estacionamientos. Casi cada centímetro de pavimento que no tiene un auto, tiene una persona."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:47
translate spanish hwb_s15b_a180916a:

    # "Also, there are different trails and forks in the road, so not everyone is going in the same direction now. Being able to drive without having to tap the brakes every couple seconds is a relief."
    "Además, hay diferentes senderos y bifurcaciones en el camino, así que ya no todos van en la misma dirección. Poder conducir sin tener que pisar el freno cada dos segundos es un alivio."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:49
translate spanish hwb_s15b_364f6d97:

    # "A pickup truck towing a trailer pulls off the shoulder ahead and back onto the road, so I take his spot."
    "Una camioneta que remolca un tráiler se sale de la banquina y vuelve a la carretera, así que tomo su lugar."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:51
translate spanish hwb_s15b_a7f891ab:

    # "Putting it in park, I take a swig of stone-cold coffee."
    "Poniéndola en estacionamiento, tomo un trago de café frío como una piedra."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:87
translate spanish hwb_s15b_19edeb76:

    # Amber "Wanna grab the pamphlets?"
    Amber "Давай глянем брошюры?"

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:89
translate spanish hwb_s15b_212a7b30:

    # "We snagged a couple of brochures back at the diner. They don’t have a whole lot of info, but they’re a starting point."
    "Conseguimos un par de folletos en el restaurante. No tienen mucha información, pero son un punto de partida."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:101
translate spanish hwb_s15b_dad430f5:

    # "Marina retrieves them and spreads them out on the table like puzzle pieces. Alongside them is the journal. Its spine has lost all strength and the pages just flop around."
    "Marina los recupera y los extiende sobre la mesa como piezas de rompecabezas. Junto a ellos está el diario. Su lomo ha perdido toda fuerza y las páginas simplemente se doblan."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:103
translate spanish hwb_s15b_4b081ebd:

    # Amber "So the journal says that it’s buried between two things."
    Amber "Так, согласно дневнику оно зарыто между двумя объектами."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:105
translate spanish hwb_s15b_7e11b4d0:

    # Marina "Right. But something out of the way."
    Marina "Да. Но где-то вне основного маршрута."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:110
translate spanish hwb_s15b_b60095a3:

    # "Peering out the windshield and to the expanses beyond… There’s a lot that could be considered \"out of the way.\""
    "Mirando a través del parabrisas hacia las extensiones más allá… Hay mucho que podría considerarse \"fuera del camino\"."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:112
translate spanish hwb_s15b_8db7fb6f:

    # Amber "It’d have to be something memorable, or else he’d come back and have no idea where to go."
    Amber "Это должно быть что-то запоминающееся, ведь иначе, по возвращению он бы сам не знал, куда идти и где искать."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:117
translate spanish hwb_s15b_b12ece6b:

    # Marina "And anything memorable is probably gonna be something popular, right?"
    Marina "И если это что-то запоминающееся, то это что-то популярное, да?"

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:121
translate spanish hwb_s15b_5352381a:

    # Amber "Exactly, yeah."
    Amber "Да, именно."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:125
translate spanish hwb_s15b_e7fb6aa3:

    # "She flips through some of the pamphlets. They all have the same information on the same landmarks, just with slightly different pictures."
    "Hojea algunos de los folletos. Todos tienen la misma información sobre los mismos lugares emblemáticos, solo con imágenes ligeramente diferentes."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:127
translate spanish hwb_s15b_7d325160:

    # Amber "Wait."
    Amber "Погоди."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:129
translate spanish hwb_s15b_6b8d83ae:

    # "She was about to toss one of them, but it catches my eye."
    "Estaba a punto de tirar uno, pero me llama la atención."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:131
translate spanish hwb_s15b_08749c24:

    # Amber "Hand me that."
    Amber "Дай-ка мне."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:133
translate spanish hwb_s15b_835bf838:

    # "Marina passes over the brochure, and I turn to one of the inner pages. It has only one picture, and a longer paragraph of text. I read aloud."
    "Marina me pasa el folleto, y yo paso a una de las páginas interiores. Tiene solo una imagen y un párrafo de texto más largo. Leo en voz alta."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:137
translate spanish hwb_s15b_57603565:

    # Amber "{i}One of the most famous landmarks in all of the park, Double Arch is a fan-favorite. Recognizable for its two elegant curves, Double Arch can be accessed via a short hike and is open to exploration!{/i}"
    Amber "{i}Одна из самых известных и любимых посетителями достопримечательностей в парке - “Двойная” арка. Ее легко узнать по двум элегантным изгибам на ней. Чтобы добраться до “Двойной” арки вам потребуется проделать небольшой поход по пересеченной местности. Арка открыта для всех любопытных исследователей!{/i}"

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:141
translate spanish hwb_s15b_cf121e4a:

    # "I hold up the flyer so she can see the picture. It’s of two huge arches of stone, connected at one side but otherwise perpendicular from each other."
    "Levanto el volante para que ella pueda ver la imagen. Son dos enormes arcos de piedra, conectados por un lado pero por lo demás perpendiculares entre sí."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:143
translate spanish hwb_s15b_0b92e2c8:

    # "She snatches it out of my hands for a closer look, nearly cutting my fingers."
    "Me lo arrebata de las manos para verlo mejor, casi cortándome los dedos."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:147
translate spanish hwb_s15b_4d47edac:

    # Marina "Oh my God, you think it’s between the two of these?"
    Marina "О боже... Ты думаешь, что оно находится между этими двумя штуками?"

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:151
translate spanish hwb_s15b_54dfd40e:

    # Amber "That’d make sense, right? You’d definitely remember how it looks. And it’s kind of out of the way."
    Amber "Это звучит логично, правда? Ты по любому запомнишь как они выглядят, но при этом они находятся вдали от дороги."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:153
translate spanish hwb_s15b_b64b5b3d:

    # "The papers whiz past my face as Marina hurls them backwards and she points forward."
    "Los papeles pasan zumbando por mi cara mientras Marina los lanza hacia atrás y señala hacia adelante."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:157
translate spanish hwb_s15b_c1d43f2d:

    # Marina "Full steam ahead!"
    Marina "Полный вперед!"

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:202
translate spanish hwb_s15b_a7718cde:

    # "I throw the RV back into drive and pull out onto the road again. There are signs everywhere for Double Arch, so we don’t need the map that we got at the gate."
    "Pongo la casa rodante de nuevo en marcha y salgo a la carretera otra vez. Hay letreros por todas partes para el Doble Arco, así que no necesitamos el mapa que conseguimos en la entrada."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:206
translate spanish hwb_s15b_6068c3a8:

    # "We pass signs for other landmarks too, some with pretty weird names. There’s the Parade of Elephants, for one thing, which is in the same direction as Ham Rock."
    "También pasamos letreros de otros lugares emblemáticos, algunos con nombres bastante extraños. Está el Desfile de Elefantes, por ejemplo, que está en la misma dirección que la Roca Jamón."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:208
translate spanish hwb_s15b_12f2c085:

    # "There’s even a phallic-sounding rock simply called The Organ."
    "Incluso hay una roca con forma fálica llamada simplemente El Órgano."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:210
translate spanish hwb_s15b_f9221394:

    # "All of those are down exits we don't take. Instead, we soon end up in the back of yet another traffic jam."
    "Todas esas son salidas hacia abajo que no tomamos. En cambio, pronto terminamos en la cola de otro embotellamiento."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:212
translate spanish hwb_s15b_0c1caa7d:

    # "Marina stares out the window as we creep along. Where we are right now is nearly indistinguishable from the highways we’ve spent so much time on."
    "Marina mira por la ventana mientras avanzamos lentamente. Donde estamos ahora es casi indistinguible de las autopistas en las que hemos pasado tanto tiempo."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:214
translate spanish hwb_s15b_0367554d:

    # "There are a few actual arches around, but none distinct enough to get any real attention."
    "Hay algunos arcos reales por aquí, pero ninguno lo suficientemente distintivo como para llamar la atención."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:216
translate spanish hwb_s15b_27fdf1ee:

    # "Inch by inch, we advance down the road until we finally come to the parking lot for Double Arch."
    "Pulgada a pulgada, avanzamos por el camino hasta que finalmente llegamos al estacionamiento del Arco Doble."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:218
translate spanish hwb_s15b_79daecd2:

    # "Only problem is, it’s totally full."
    "El único problema es que está completamente lleno."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:220
translate spanish hwb_s15b_fd06599c:

    # "Not just busy, but packed. Every parking spot is taken, with a few cars jammed into empty space that’s clearly not meant for that."
    "No solo concurrido, sino abarrotado. Cada espacio de estacionamiento está ocupado, con algunos autos metidos en espacios vacíos que claramente no están diseñados para eso."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:222
translate spanish hwb_s15b_fb97d355:

    # "Like lice, people swarm up and down the arch itself, visible even from the road. At least this time it isn’t off-limits."
    "Como piojos, la gente pulula arriba y abajo del arco, visible incluso desde la carretera. Al menos esta vez no está prohibido el acceso."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:226
translate spanish hwb_s15b_4bdd3eba:

    # Marina "Looks like everyone else had the same idea."
    Marina "Похоже, все остальные тут за тем же, за чем и мы."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:230
translate spanish hwb_s15b_2a74b23f:

    # Amber "Don’t sound so glum. We can still go take a look."
    Amber "Не унывай. Как минимум, мы можем просто пойти глянуть."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:234
translate spanish hwb_s15b_3956d3b8:

    # Marina "If we can ever find somewhere to park."
    Marina "Если мы когда-нибудь найдем, где запарковаться."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:238
translate spanish hwb_s15b_7d12c9ce:

    # Amber "Yeah, that is a pretty big 'if.'"
    Amber "Мда. Это очень существенное “если”."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:240
translate spanish hwb_s15b_fea5d165:

    # "The entire caravan passes by the parking lot. There’s at least a dozen cars behind me, too."
    "Toda la caravana pasa por el estacionamiento. También hay al menos una docena de autos detrás de mí."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:242
translate spanish hwb_s15b_002b1599:

    # "Maybe a half mile up the road, we come across another lot."
    "Tal vez a media milla por el camino, nos encontramos con otro estacionamiento."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:246
translate spanish hwb_s15b_ed876739:

    # Amber "Up for a bit of walking?"
    Amber "Готова немного пройтись?"

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:250
translate spanish hwb_s15b_ca73936a:

    # Marina "Yeah!"
    Marina "Да!"

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:256
translate spanish hwb_s15b_d5aa2d22:

    # "I quickly take one of the remaining spaces. There are a few openings here. Looks like most people weren’t as willing to walk as Marina is."
    "Rápidamente tomo uno de los espacios restantes. Hay algunos lugares libres aquí. Parece que la mayoría de la gente no estaba tan dispuesta a caminar como Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:258
translate spanish hwb_s15b_2e685c6c:

    # "Some of the cars behind us pull in, too."
    "Algunos de los autos detrás de nosotros también se estacionan."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:305
translate spanish hwb_s15b_6fcf2dbd:

    # "We opt to leave the metal detector and other equipment in the RV for now. If we see anything that looks promising, we can come back and grab it."
    "Optamos por dejar el detector de metales y el resto del equipo en la casa rodante por ahora. Si vemos algo prometedor, podemos regresar a buscarlo."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:307
translate spanish hwb_s15b_227c4e00:

    # "The walk back up to Double Arch doesn’t take long. And it’s nice to be outdoors again."
    "La caminata de regreso al Arco Doble no toma mucho tiempo. Y es agradable estar al aire libre de nuevo."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:309
translate spanish hwb_s15b_1cd80b0e:

    # "We have to stick to the very edge of the road to avoid the stream of cars flowing towards us. Seems there was more than a dozen behind us after all."
    "Tenemos que pegarnos al borde del camino para evitar el flujo de autos que vienen hacia nosotros. Parece que había más de una docena detrás de nosotros después de todo."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:311
translate spanish hwb_s15b_192e630b:

    # "There’s a short hike from the Double Arch parking lot to the arch itself. It’s an easy one, and we don’t even break a sweat."
    "Hay una caminata corta desde el estacionamiento del Arco Doble hasta el arco en sí. Es fácil, y ni siquiera sudamos."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:313
translate spanish hwb_s15b_a2170402:

    # "Up close, it’s obvious that there aren’t many people here just to see the sights. Almost everyone is carrying a shovel or other tool."
    "De cerca, es obvio que no hay mucha gente aquí solo para ver las vistas. Casi todos llevan una pala u otra herramienta."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:315
translate spanish hwb_s15b_befbe2f7:

    # "There’s a pair of park rangers watching, but they don’t seem to be intervening at all. They just slouch against a wooden fence, looking defeated."
    "Hay un par de guardabosques vigilando, pero no parecen intervenir en absoluto. Solo se recuestan contra una cerca de madera, con aspecto derrotado."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:320
translate spanish hwb_s15b_b95a5d91:

    # Amber "Can you imagine how big of celebrities we’d be if anyone here knew we found the Shiprock treasure?"
    Amber "Представь, как бы мы стали знамениты в этой компании, если бы они прознали, что это мы нашли сокровища возле Шипрок?"

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:322
translate spanish hwb_s15b_a5399526:

    # "I whisper as quietly as I can to Marina."
    "Susurro lo más bajo que puedo a Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:327
translate spanish hwb_s15b_7d27bd23:

    # Marina "Right? I was thinking about that earlier. I kinda wanted to show off, but that’s probably not a good idea."
    Marina "Ага. Я думала об этом ранее и даже подумывала раскрыть карты, но, наверное, это не самая лучшая идея."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:331
translate spanish hwb_s15b_109d80e8:

    # Amber "Like anyone would believe us, anyway. But you don’t want to have your face all over the New York Times as one of the girls who found the treasure?"
    Amber "Как будто бы кто-то нам поверит. И тебе не хочется быть на фотке в Нью-Йорк Таймс, как одной из девчонок, которые нашли сокровище?"

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:335
translate spanish hwb_s15b_c4d13579:

    # Marina "Hmm… Being in the local newspaper is on my bucket list."
    Marina "Хммм…  В мои планы входит оказаться в местной газете."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:339
translate spanish hwb_s15b_f95ee322:

    # "Dream big, Marina."
    "Sueña en grande, Marina."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:341
translate spanish hwb_s15b_10847f1a:

    # Marina "And my friends from school would totally have a heart attack when they found out."
    Marina "А мои друзья из школы получат сердечный приступ, когда узнают обо всем."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:345
translate spanish hwb_s15b_50ed93f7:

    # Marina "But don’t they always say to keep it a secret if you win the lottery?"
    Marina "Но, разве не говорят, что надо хранить тайну, если ты выиграл в лотерею?"

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:349
translate spanish hwb_s15b_27808ad7:

    # Amber "Yeah, otherwise people will never leave you alone. You’ll get all sorts of messages from people you used to know or long lost relatives."
    Amber "Ага, иначе от тебя никогда не отстанут. Тебе начнут спамить сообщениями люди, которых ты когда-то знала или какие-то далекие-далекие родственники."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:353
translate spanish hwb_s15b_6184ac10:

    # Marina "Ugh, I have enough not-lost relatives to deal with."
    Marina "Угу, у меня и так хватает “далеких-далеких” родственников, с которыми приходится иметь дело."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:357
translate spanish hwb_s15b_d83e4185:

    # Marina "Plus, I don’t wanna get kidnapped and held for ransom or something like that."
    Marina "И еще я не хочу, чтобы меня похитили и требовали выкуп или типа того."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:361
translate spanish hwb_s15b_76aab332:

    # Marina "What about you?"
    Marina "А что на счет тебя?"

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:369
translate spanish hwb_s15b_60a10cf2:

    # Amber "Based on the current market rates for gold going at $40,000 per kilo and assuming this is gold is of decent purity, I'll probably put my share of the gold into a low-cost index fund."
    Amber "Учитывая текущее состояние рынков и то, что за килограмм золота дают $40,000 и предполагая, что это золото - высшей пробы, я, наверное, вложу его на фондовую биржу."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:373
translate spanish hwb_s15b_4ec988ca:

    # Amber "Given that most index funds average around a 10 percent rate of return in the long-term, I can take care of all expenses and still have a solid investment for retirement."
    Amber "Учитывая, что подобные вложения приносят около 10%% годовых, в долгосрочной перспективе я смогу покрыть все свои затраты, но при этом сохранить эти инвестиции на будущее."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:377
translate spanish hwb_s15b_bad46fb8:

    # Marina "{cps=3}...{/cps}{w=0.5}That's really fascinating Amber."
    Marina "{cps=3}...{/cps}{w=0.5}Это очень интересно, Эмбер."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:390
translate spanish hwb_s15b_6d10d619:

    # Amber "A solid foundation for a future is always fascinating."
    Amber "Вкладывать в свое будущее - всегда интересно."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:396
translate spanish hwb_s15b_331020ca:

    # Amber "No way. I’m just gonna quietly retreat into one of my three mansions when all this is over."
    Amber "Но нет, конечно. Я просто тихо перееду в один из своих трех особняков, когда мы закончим с этим всем."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:398
translate spanish hwb_s15b_cf28d0be:

    # Marina "Oh, you’re only gonna buy three?"
    Marina "О, ты купишь всего лишь три?"

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:402
translate spanish hwb_s15b_44e7f489:

    # Amber "Yeah, gotta save the rest for my fourteen new motorhomes, after all."
    Amber "Ага, мне же нужно сохранить остальную часть денег на покупку четырнадцати новых трейлеров."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:406
translate spanish hwb_s15b_8f6c5e0e:

    # "She giggles."
    "Ella ríe entre dientes."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:410
translate spanish hwb_s15b_e49a77ac:

    # Marina "Do I get to drive one of them?"
    Marina "А мне можно будет поводить один из них?"

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:414
translate spanish hwb_s15b_a1dc3cde:

    # Amber "Why not? But you could buy your own, you know."
    Amber "Почему нет? Хотя, знаешь, ты могла бы купить себе свой."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:418
translate spanish hwb_s15b_b31a1a79:

    # Marina "No way. I’ll just come bother you if I need one."
    Marina "Не вариант. Я просто буду доставать тебя, если мне вдруг понадобиться трейлер."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:420
translate spanish hwb_s15b_9fb0fefc:

    # "We’ve gotten as close to the arches as we can. The mob of sweaty people is too thick for us to push our way through. There are dozens of people sweeping over the dusty ground with metal detectors."
    "Nos hemos acercado lo más posible a los arcos. La multitud sudorosa es demasiado densa para que podamos abrirnos paso. Hay docenas de personas barriendo el suelo polvoriento con detectores de metales."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:422
translate spanish hwb_s15b_b879c64d:

    # "Hanging back around the edge, Marina’s smile fades away quickly."
    "Quedándome atrás en el borde, la sonrisa de Marina se desvanece rápidamente."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:426
translate spanish hwb_s15b_e7c0bba1:

    # Marina "Um…"
    Marina "Эм…"

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:430
translate spanish hwb_s15b_8f33dbf4:

    # Amber "Yeah, this is a bit of a mess."
    Amber "Ага, это просто бардак какой-то."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:433
translate spanish hwb_s15b_61515347:

    # "People Joshle and push each other out of the way. It’s hard to believe anyone is actually prospecting so much as they are just trying not to lose their spot."
    "La gente se empuja y se aparta del camino. Es difícil creer que alguien esté realmente prospectando tanto como tratando de no perder su lugar."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:436
translate spanish hwb_s15b_e78e5ab0:

    # "People jostle and push each other out of the way. It’s hard to believe anyone is actually prospecting so much as they are just trying not to lose their spot."
    "La gente se empuja y se aparta del camino. Es difícil creer que alguien esté realmente prospectando tanto como tratando de no perder su lugar."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:438
translate spanish hwb_s15b_b8d7c014:

    # Marina "Maybe we should come back later?"
    Marina "Может нам стоит прийти попозже?"

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:440
translate spanish hwb_s15b_eca9a1b0:

    # "I don’t know if it’ll be any better later, but maybe."
    "No sé si después estará mejor, pero tal vez."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:444
translate spanish hwb_s15b_8f5fc9ff:

    # Amber "I guess. Though if the treasure is here, I feel like someone would’ve found it by now."
    Amber "Пожалуй. Но если сокровище тут, то его бы по любому уже кто-то нашел."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:446
translate spanish hwb_s15b_b0c4d47b:

    # "Just like back at Canyon de Chelly."
    "Igual que en Canyon de Chelly."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:450
translate spanish hwb_s15b_cdb0c80b:

    # Amber "You know this must have been going on for a few days now."
    Amber "Знаешь, а ведь такое творится уже несколько дней."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:454
translate spanish hwb_s15b_8b587bb4:

    # Marina "Yeah…"
    Marina "Ага…"

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:456
translate spanish hwb_s15b_79e43187:

    # "All the enthusiasm she had just a minute ago when we were joking around has evaporated in the desert sun."
    "Todo el entusiasmo que tenía hace un momento cuando bromeábamos se ha evaporado bajo el sol del desierto."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:458
translate spanish hwb_s15b_dc8449c5:

    # "A rock skips past my foot as she kicks at the dirt."
    "Una piedra pasa rozando mi pie mientras ella patea la tierra."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:468
translate spanish hwb_s15b_dcd09c09:

    # "I poke her, and she yelps in surprise."
    "Le doy un toque y ella da un grito de sorpresa."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:472
translate spanish hwb_s15b_06c8c21c:

    # Amber "Hey now. I’m not saying we give up. I’m just saying we regroup and strategize. We can go see the rest of the park in the meantime."
    Amber "Ну же. Я не говорю, что мы сдаемся. Я говорю, что нам нужно перегруппироваться и действовать тактично. А пока можно осмотреть парк."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:474
translate spanish hwb_s15b_5a7df71e:

    # Amber "Didn’t you say you’ve wanted to see this place for a while?"
    Amber "Разве ты не говорила, что давно хотела тут побывать?"

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:478
translate spanish hwb_s15b_d2c76cb0:

    # Marina "Yeah, I guess."
    Marina "Ну да, наверное."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:480
translate spanish hwb_s15b_53926654:

    # "It’s obvious that she’s still bummed, but there's nothing I can do about that."
    "Es obvio que todavía está desanimada, pero no puedo hacer nada al respecto."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:486
translate spanish hwb_s15b_03376252:

    # "Once we’re back in the motorhome, we leave the busy main road ASAP and spend a while seeing the sights from our air conditioned comfort."
    "Una vez de vuelta en la casa rodante, salimos de la carretera principal concurrida lo antes posible y pasamos un rato viendo los paisajes desde la comodidad del aire acondicionado."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:488
translate spanish hwb_s15b_ac0938c0:

    # "Marina’s mood improves steadily throughout the day, counteracted only by our growing hunger."
    "El ánimo de Marina mejora constantemente durante el día, solo contrarrestado por nuestro creciente hambre."

# game/script/hwb_s15b.rpy:490
translate spanish hwb_s15b_eae87b15:

    # "As we pull back into Moab, we're both ravenous."
    "Cuando llegamos de vuelta a Moab, ambas estamos famélicas."

